Rapid Transfer is an Ecobank proprietary send and receive money transfer product available in all Ecobank location across Africa.This unique product facilitates easy transfer and access to funds across Nigeria and in all countries where Ecobank is present.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .